                           <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__anna_QGW_II_I_1609"><add>anstatt</add></roleName></rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="pe__elisabeth_QGW_II_I_1609">Els, dessen <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__friedrich_tischler_QGW_II_I_1609">Schwester</roleName> und <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__stephan_fraunschuechl_QGW_II_I_1609"><add>wittib</add></roleName>
                           <rs type="person" ref="pe__stephan_fraunschuechl_QGW_II_I_1609">Stephans
