                              <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__christine_QGW_II_I_1609">anstatt</roleName>
                           <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__anna_QGW_II_I_1609"><add>anstatt</add></roleName></rs></rs></unclear> der <rs type="person" ref="pe__christine_QGW_II_I_1609"><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__friedrich_tischler_QGW_II_I_1609">unmündigen
                        Töchter</roleName> des Tischlers Christein</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__anna_QGW_II_I_1609"><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__friedrich_tischler_QGW_II_I_1609"><add>unmündigen
